  "notes": "Post Partum File 3, Group A (BP measured during PNC visits). Split config over the 'a' sheets (Q1a-Q4a); paired Group B (high-BP referral) is post_hpn_mgmt over the 'b' sheets (decision D3). Municipality level (66 ingested rows; region skipped). 3 meta cols; location NAME col 2. Chained same-bracket denominator; fixed & logged (v2). No DQC columns in source; over-100% rule is ours. Annual sheets are pure rollups, not ingested."
